# Tooltips — Item Pipes
# %1$s = transfer size, %2$s = tick rate
rusticpipes.tooltip.pipe.data=Transfers %1$s item(s) every %2$s tick(s) when unpowered.
rusticpipes.tooltip.pipe.description.white_pipe=Place these pipes between two containers and configure their connections to be either input (yellow) or output (red) arrows on the flanges of the pipe. Transfers at a slow rate when unpowered but can be upgraded by connecting a network to a pipe motor. These pipes can be dyed to different colors to make them not connect, either by crafting them in a specific color or right clicking them with a dye.
