# Tooltips — Conduit (Power Cord)
# %1$s = FE per tick per face
rusticpipes.tooltip.conduit.data=Transfers up to %1$s FE per tick.
rusticpipes.tooltip.conduit.description=Power cord to transfer power from a power source to a power consumer. These cables attract lightning when powered and exposed to the elements, shows red/white particles when power is being transferred and can be right clicked at their connections to display their power level.

# Tooltips — Pipe Motors
# %1$s = transfer size, %2$s = tick rate, %3$s = FE cost per transfer
rusticpipes.tooltip.pipemotor.slow.data=[Basic] Transfers %1$s item(s) every %2$s tick(s) costing %3$s FE per transfer.
rusticpipes.tooltip.pipemotor.slow.description=Place this Basic pipe motor block next to one or multiple item pipe networks to enable powered item transfer. Consumes a small amount of energy per transfer cycle.

rusticpipes.tooltip.pipemotor.normal.data=[Refined] Transfers %1$s item(s) every %2$s tick(s) costing %3$s FE per transfer.
rusticpipes.tooltip.pipemotor.normal.description=Place this Refined pipe motor block next to one or multiple item pipe networks to make item transfer faster. Consumes more energy than the Basic motor.

rusticpipes.tooltip.pipemotor.fast.data=[Efficient] Transfers %1$s item(s) every %2$s tick(s) costing %3$s FE per transfer.
rusticpipes.tooltip.pipemotor.fast.description=Place this Efficient pipe motor block next to one or multiple item pipe networks to make item transfer significantly faster. Balances speed and energy consumption.

rusticpipes.tooltip.pipemotor.turbo.data=[Advanced] Transfers %1$s item(s) every %2$s tick(s) costing %3$s FE per transfer.
rusticpipes.tooltip.pipemotor.turbo.description=Place this Advanced pipe motor block next to one or multiple item pipe networks to make item transfer much faster but also consume considerably more energy.

rusticpipes.tooltip.pipemotor.hyper.data=[Reinforced] Transfers %1$s item(s) every %2$s tick(s) costing %3$s FE per transfer.
rusticpipes.tooltip.pipemotor.hyper.description=Place this Reinforced pipe motor block next to one or multiple item pipe networks for high-speed item transfer. Requires a substantial power supply to operate.

rusticpipes.tooltip.pipemotor.ultra.data=[Ultra] Transfers %1$s item(s) every %2$s tick(s) costing %3$s FE per transfer.
rusticpipes.tooltip.pipemotor.ultra.description=Place this Ultra/Overclocked pipe motor block next to one or multiple item pipe networks to make item transfer between containers faster but also consume more energy.
